305
00:24:41,815 --> 00:24:44,985
ls there something you'd like to tell us?

306
00:24:47,571 --> 00:24:51,241
Are you accusing me of knowing
something that I'm not telling you?

307
00:24:51,325 --> 00:24:55,162
