<i>Hey, you look great. You look great.</i>

320
00:25:55,556 --> 00:25:57,891
<i>Hey, Gar.</i>

321
00:25:57,975 --> 00:26:00,436
<i>Mom, I got some great news.</i>

322
00:26:00,519 --> 00:26:02,604
<i>- Me too.
- You first.</i>

323
00:26:03,605 --> 00:26:05,691
<i>I quit. I'm clean as a whistle.</i>

324
00:26:06,775 --> 00:26:10,779
Brought you your favourite.
You finish your movie.

325
00:26:10,863 --> 00:26:13,240
Don't stay up too late. OK, son?

326
00:26:15,367 --> 00:26:18,787
<i>- Well, that's a start.
- Well, what about your news?</i>

327
00:26:19,830 --> 00:26:23,542
<i>Well, it's no big deal.
I met a girl. We're goin' out.</i>

328
00:26:23,625 --> 00:26:26,628
<i>Oh! Come on, tell us!</i>

329
00:26:26,712 --> 00:26:28,964
<i>- Well, her name is Diana.
- Yeah?</i>

330
00:26:29,047 --> 00:26:31,842
<i>- She's beautiful, with long blonde hair.
- Yeah?</i>

331
00:26:31,925 --> 00:26:34,887
<i>She rides horses,
and she's beautiful and she's smart,</i>

332
00:26:34,970 --> 00:26:37,222
<i>and she loves me.</i>

333
00:26:37,973 --> 00:26:41,560
<i>Oh, what's not to love, baby?</i>

334
